{
  "id": "65d347ec485ae30025583034",
  "title": "光る君へ 第三回「謎の男」",
  "created": 1708345338,
  "updated": 1708347969,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "65d347ec485ae30025583034",
      "text": "光る君へ 第三回「謎の男」",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708345338,
      "updated": 1708345338
    },
    {
      "id": "65d347fa5e90c0000059618c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708345338,
      "updated": 1708345338
    },
    {
      "id": "65d347fa5e90c0000059618d",
      "text": ">自分のせいで放免に捕らえられた道長（[柄本佑]）を心配するまひろ（吉高由里子）。しかし、父の為時（岸谷五朗）に謹慎を強いられたため、ただ案じることしかできない。兼家（段田安則）の指示で道兼（玉置玲央）は女官を使って帝の食事に毒を仕込み、円融天皇（坂東巳之助）は急激に体が弱っていく。政権を掌握するために二の手を打ちたい兼家は、ライバルの左大臣家の動向を探るため、為時を利用してまひろを間者として送り込む。",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708345338,
      "updated": 1708345468
    },
    {
      "id": "65d3481c5e90c00000596190",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708345372,
      "updated": 1708345372
    },
    {
      "id": "65d3481c5e90c00000596191",
      "text": "[放免]に捕まる三郎なのであった（前回のあらすじ）",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708345372,
      "updated": 1708345443
    },
    {
      "id": "65d347fa5e90c0000059618e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708345338,
      "updated": 1708345338
    },
    {
      "id": "65d348665e90c00000596195",
      "text": "OP",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708345446,
      "updated": 1708345446
    },
    {
      "id": "65d348a65e90c00000596196",
      "text": " 今回人がおすすめしていた[源倫子]が出てくるらしい[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708345510,
      "updated": 1708345529
    },
    {
      "id": "65d348ba5e90c00000596197",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708345530,
      "updated": 1708345530
    },
    {
      "id": "65d348ba5e90c00000596198",
      "text": "無罪放免三郎",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708345530,
      "updated": 1708345616
    },
    {
      "id": "65d349135e90c00000596199",
      "text": " 高貴な身分であることが明らかになった",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708345618,
      "updated": 1708345631
    },
    {
      "id": "65d3491f5e90c0000059619a",
      "text": "  覗く人が一人",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708345631,
      "updated": 1708345635
    },
    {
      "id": "65d349245e90c0000059619b",
      "text": " 兼家に滅茶苦茶怒られる",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708345635,
      "updated": 1708345649
    },
    {
      "id": "65d349565e90c0000059619c",
      "text": "  [藤原詮子]も東三条の邸宅に帰ってきたようだ[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708345686,
      "updated": 1708345730
    },
    {
      "id": "65d349825e90c0000059619d",
      "text": "   かなしみ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708345730,
      "updated": 1708345734
    },
    {
      "id": "65d349855e90c0000059619e",
      "text": " 道長が下々の娘に懸想している話がバレている",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708345734,
      "updated": 1708345811
    },
    {
      "id": "65d349d35e90c0000059619f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708345811,
      "updated": 1708345847
    },
    {
      "id": "65d349f75e90c000005961a0",
      "text": "まひろサイド",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708345847,
      "updated": 1708345857
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34a015e90c000005961a2",
      "text": " にしても三郎のことが思い出される",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708345857,
      "updated": 1708345869
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34a0d5e90c000005961a3",
      "text": "  キテる",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708345869,
      "updated": 1708345873
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34a115e90c000005961a4",
      "text": " 月を見るだけという話",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708345873,
      "updated": 1708345891
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34a255e90c000005961a5",
      "text": "  朧月夜ポイント+1",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708345893,
      "updated": 1708345900
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34a385e90c000005961a6",
      "text": " 謎の男登場",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708345912,
      "updated": 1708345917
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34a3e5e90c000005961a7",
      "text": "  誰？",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708345917,
      "updated": 1708345921
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34a4e5e90c000005961a8",
      "text": "  [光る君へ 第二回「めぐりあい」]でぶつかった人らしい",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708345934,
      "updated": 1708345953
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34a875e90c000005961a9",
      "text": " 絵は下手",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708345991,
      "updated": 1708345995
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34a8b5e90c000005961aa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708345995,
      "updated": 1708345995
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34a8b5e90c000005961ab",
      "text": "碁タイム",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708345995,
      "updated": 1708346003
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34a935e90c000005961ac",
      "text": " 道長・[藤原公任]・[藤原忠信]の",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708346003,
      "updated": 1708346124
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34ab55e90c000005961ad",
      "text": "  何かを読み出す",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708346036,
      "updated": 1708346051
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34ac45e90c000005961ae",
      "text": "  歌の良し悪しを色々言う",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708346051,
      "updated": 1708346096
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34ad05e90c000005961af",
      "text": "   雨夜の品定めポイント+1",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708346064,
      "updated": 1708346112
    },
    {
      "id": "65d347fa5e90c0000059618f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708345338,
      "updated": 1708346209
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34b615e90c000005961b0",
      "text": "三郎探索タイム",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708346209,
      "updated": 1708346214
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34b665e90c000005961b1",
      "text": " 馬上のその人がそれなんですよね",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708346214,
      "updated": 1708346226
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34b925e90c000005961b2",
      "text": "  全員違いました[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708346258,
      "updated": 1708346271
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34ba05e90c000005961b3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708346272,
      "updated": 1708346304
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34bc05e90c000005961b4",
      "text": "安倍晴明の祈祷タイムも効果なく[円融天皇]のお体がどんどん悪くなっていく",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708346304,
      "updated": 1708346342
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34be75e90c000005961b6",
      "text": " [藤原実資]と[道兼]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708346343,
      "updated": 1708346359
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34c245e90c000005961b9",
      "text": " 食事に見聞を図る[蔵人頭]するどい[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708346404,
      "updated": 1708346424
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34c235e90c000005961b8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708346402,
      "updated": 1708346426
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34c875e90c000005961ba",
      "text": "て、[定子]様！[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708346503,
      "updated": 1708346521
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34c9f5e90c000005961bb",
      "text": " [道隆]の娘",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708346527,
      "updated": 1708346563
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34cad5e90c000005961bc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708346541,
      "updated": 1708346560
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34cc15e90c000005961bd",
      "text": "安倍晴明の仕事も済んだ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708346561,
      "updated": 1708346590
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34cde5e90c000005961c0",
      "text": " 円融天皇が譲位すべきかどうか悩む",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708346590,
      "updated": 1708346610
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34d225e90c000005961c1",
      "text": "  自らの子を東宮にしたい、という点で兼家と利害が一致する",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708346658,
      "updated": 1708346699
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34d4b5e90c000005961c2",
      "text": "  はてさてどうなる？[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708346699,
      "updated": 1708346703
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34cc15e90c000005961be",
      "text": " [師貞親王]は眼中にない",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708346561,
      "updated": 1708346723
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34d715e90c000005961c3",
      "text": " むちゃくちゃ疑う円融天皇",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708346737,
      "updated": 1708346744
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34db05e90c000005961c5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708346800,
      "updated": 1708346800
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34db75e90c000005961c6",
      "text": "定例噂話",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708346807,
      "updated": 1708346811
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34dbd5e90c000005961c7",
      "text": " 女房たちが毒を盛ったと疑われたのを憤慨している",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708346813,
      "updated": 1708346860
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34dbe5e90c000005961c8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708346814,
      "updated": 1708346814
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34dee5e90c000005961c9",
      "text": "道兼と道長の微妙な雰囲気",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708346861,
      "updated": 1708346906
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34e1b5e90c000005961ca",
      "text": " >一献傾けたいな",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708346907,
      "updated": 1708346919
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34e285e90c000005961cb",
      "text": "  多分この日は来ない[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708346920,
      "updated": 1708346926
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34e2f5e90c000005961cc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708346927,
      "updated": 1708346927
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34e2f5e90c000005961cd",
      "text": "兼家・為時話",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708346927,
      "updated": 1708346966
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34e555e90c000005961ce",
      "text": " [師貞親王]は見違えるように勉強しているよ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708346966,
      "updated": 1708347026
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34cc25e90c000005961bf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708346561,
      "updated": 1708346561
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34e705e90c000005961cf",
      "text": "[土御門殿]・左大臣[源定信]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708346992,
      "updated": 1708347063
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34e7e5e90c000005961d1",
      "text": " そしてその娘[源倫子]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347006,
      "updated": 1708347017
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34e945e90c000005961d2",
      "text": "  琴をやっている",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347028,
      "updated": 1708347037
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34e9d5e90c000005961d3",
      "text": "  御年22だそうで",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347037,
      "updated": 1708347068
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34e745e90c000005961d0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708346996,
      "updated": 1708346996
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34ec55e90c000005961d4",
      "text": "左大臣の北の方に歌のサロンがあるので行けとまひろにいう為時",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347077,
      "updated": 1708347126
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34ed15e90c000005961d6",
      "text": " [赤染衛門]！[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347089,
      "updated": 1708347097
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34efd5e90c000005961d7",
      "text": " 来ました[土御門殿]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347133,
      "updated": 1708347142
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34f075e90c000005961d8",
      "text": "  もう建物が豪奢",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347143,
      "updated": 1708347151
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34f105e90c000005961d9",
      "text": "  集まった人々にオーラがある",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347152,
      "updated": 1708347163
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34f335e90c000005961da",
      "text": " あら、官職がないの……という雰囲気、辛",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347187,
      "updated": 1708347204
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34f4a5e90c000005961db",
      "text": " 「へんつぎ」というのをするらしい",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347210,
      "updated": 1708347245
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34f745e90c000005961dc",
      "text": "  作りを示すので偏をあげる遊びである",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347252,
      "updated": 1708347287
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34f985e90c000005961dd",
      "text": "  漢字強い勢には楽勝の遊び",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347287,
      "updated": 1708347321
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34fb95e90c000005961de",
      "text": "   なお場の空気",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347321,
      "updated": 1708347326
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34fe15e90c000005961df",
      "text": "   [一人でやってるよ～]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347361,
      "updated": 1708347367
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34fe55e90c000005961e0",
      "text": "   出禁だろうこんなの[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347365,
      "updated": 1708347390
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34ffc5e90c000005961e2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347388,
      "updated": 1708347408
    },
    {
      "id": "65d350105e90c000005961e3",
      "text": "貴公子勉学コーナー",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347408,
      "updated": 1708347418
    },
    {
      "id": "65d3501a5e90c000005961e4",
      "text": " 孟子の話",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347418,
      "updated": 1708347424
    },
    {
      "id": "65d350205e90c000005961e5",
      "text": "  公任は余裕",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347424,
      "updated": 1708347429
    },
    {
      "id": "65d350375e90c000005961e6",
      "text": "  道長は無理",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347447,
      "updated": 1708347455
    },
    {
      "id": "65d3503f5e90c000005961e7",
      "text": " 上級貴族は研鑽が必要なんだなあ[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347455,
      "updated": 1708347480
    },
    {
      "id": "65d350595e90c000005961e8",
      "text": " 今度は写経（経ではなく漢詩）",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347481,
      "updated": 1708347504
    },
    {
      "id": "65d34ff25e90c000005961e1",
      "text": "  後の[藤原行成]も登場しました",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347378,
      "updated": 1708347535
    },
    {
      "id": "65d350855e90c000005961e9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347525,
      "updated": 1708347525
    },
    {
      "id": "65d350905e90c000005961ea",
      "text": "まひろコーナー",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347536,
      "updated": 1708347541
    },
    {
      "id": "65d350985e90c000005961ec",
      "text": " 為時に報告",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347544,
      "updated": 1708347559
    },
    {
      "id": "65d350ac5e90c000005961ed",
      "text": "  [- なんじゃいワシを間者として使おうってか]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347564,
      "updated": 1708347637
    },
    {
      "id": "65d350f65e90c000005961ee",
      "text": "  とは言わず継続して向かう予定",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347638,
      "updated": 1708347648
    },
    {
      "id": "65d351005e90c000005961ef",
      "text": "  内心は怒りがうずまくまひろ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347648,
      "updated": 1708347661
    },
    {
      "id": "65d3510e5e90c000005961f0",
      "text": "   そらあねえ……[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347662,
      "updated": 1708347667
    },
    {
      "id": "65d351135e90c000005961f1",
      "text": "   でも",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347667,
      "updated": 1708347669
    },
    {
      "id": "65d351165e90c000005961f2",
      "text": " 古今集",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347670,
      "updated": 1708347687
    },
    {
      "id": "65d351285e90c000005961f3",
      "text": "  >見てもまたまたもみまくのほしければなるるを人のいとふべらなり",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347688,
      "updated": 1708347716
    },
    {
      "id": "65d351445e90c000005961f4",
      "text": "   人の　歌を　詠んだら　どろぼう！",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347716,
      "updated": 1708347747
    },
    {
      "id": "65d351545e90c000005961f5",
      "text": "  赤染衛門は古今集を全て覚えているらしい",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347732,
      "updated": 1708347776
    },
    {
      "id": "65d351805e90c000005961f6",
      "text": "   強い[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347776,
      "updated": 1708347778
    },
    {
      "id": "65d350925e90c000005961eb",
      "text": " [散楽]タイム",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347538,
      "updated": 1708347815
    },
    {
      "id": "65d351a85e90c000005961f8",
      "text": "  ここにも三郎の姿はなし",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347816,
      "updated": 1708347827
    },
    {
      "id": "65d351bf5e90c000005961f9",
      "text": "  遭遇する二人（三郎とまひろ）",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347839,
      "updated": 1708347883
    },
    {
      "id": "65d351ec5e90c000005961fa",
      "text": "   キテる……",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347883,
      "updated": 1708347890
    },
    {
      "id": "65d351f25e90c000005961fb",
      "text": "    けどこの男の兄が母を殺してるんスよね[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347890,
      "updated": 1708347903
    },
    {
      "id": "65d351945e90c000005961f7",
      "text": "  謎の男は散楽師だったらしい",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347796,
      "updated": 1708347945
    },
    {
      "id": "65d3522c5e90c000005961fd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347948,
      "updated": 1708347948
    },
    {
      "id": "65d3522d5e90c000005961fe",
      "text": "つづく→[光る君へ 第四回「五節の舞姫」]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347948,
      "updated": 1708347969
    },
    {
      "id": "65d3520e5e90c000005961fc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1708347919,
      "updated": 1708347919
    }
  ]
}